  "title": "Digimod [Cobblemon][NeoForge/Fabric]",
  "description": "Implements Digimon into Cobblemon",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8qPLUWu.png\" width=\"564\" height=\"282\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j9GaXNI.png\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://codderg.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Wiki-Read-2ea44f?logo=wikipedia&amp;logoColor=white&amp;style=flat&amp;labelColor=111\" alt=\"Wiki\" width=\"266\" height=\"61\"></a> &nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/j2mfpBHXwt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/dynamic/json?url=https://discord.com/api/guilds/1086809193878655057/widget.json&amp;query=presence_count&amp;style=flat&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Discord&amp;color=5865F2&amp;labelColor=111\" alt=\"Discord\" width=\"311\" height=\"59\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/digimod-cobblemon\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/digimod-cobblemon?logo=modrinth&amp;labelColor=black&amp;color=1bd96a\" alt=\"Modrinth Downloads\" width=\"369\" height=\"63\"></a> &nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/themodderg/projects\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/1431756?logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=eb622b&amp;labelColor=black&amp;color=eb622b\" alt=\"CurseForge Downloads\" width=\"349\" height=\"64\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">Digimod [Cobblemon]</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\"> is a large-scale Cobblemon addon that replaces Pok&eacute;mon with </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">202 fully implemented Digimon</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">, transforming the Cobblemon experience into a Digimon-focused world. All Pok&eacute;mon spawns are disabled and fully replaced by Digimon, creating a Digimon-only gameplay experience.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">Each Digimon features </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">customized move sets adapted from Cobblemon mechanics</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">, with </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">rebalanced and modified stats</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\"> designed to better match Digimon lore and power scaling. Progression follows canonical Digimon evolution stages: </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">Baby I (Baby), Baby II (In-Training), Child (Rookie), Adult (Champion), and Perfect (Ultimate)</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">. </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">Mega evolutions are <span style=\"color: #fff;\">not yet available</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">This addon is heavily inspired by </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">ModderG&rsquo;s <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/the-digimod-beta\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">The Digimod</a></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">. Models and textures are provided by&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">Modder G</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\"> and the </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">Digimod Discord community</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">.</span></span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3 style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #fff; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">Version 1.3 and big 1.21.1 update ( not that big ):&nbsp;<br><br></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">Now grant total of 40 Digimon have been fully re-animated. </span></span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">Starters are now included in the mod file, no need to access config.</span></span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">Pok&eacute; Balls have been&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">retextured into V-Pets</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">, but still use </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">Pok&eacute; Ball 3D models</span></span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">Full V-Pet models are planned for a future update</span></span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">There is&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">no planned release yet for a version where Cobblemon Pok&eacute;mon spawn alongside Digimon</span></span>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">A </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">separate version is planned</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\"> that will allow both Pok&eacute;mon and Digimon to coexist</span></span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">This version will not be balanced</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">, as the main development focus remains </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">Digimon-only content</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; color: #000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\"><br></span></span></span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">For now there is a datapack available for this on Digimod discord server for both 1.20.1 and 1.21.1</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">1.20.1 will no longer be in development moving forward</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">For Nether/End Spawning lower vanilla mobs spawn for some reason NeoForge likes to spawn so many there preventing cobblemon spawns</span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; text-decoration: none;\">Digimon that can be ridden:<br><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1431756/description_f384bc0a-6a54-405c-b458-8752368b2d5c.png\"><br><br><em>List Below:&nbsp;</em><br>Infermon<br>Ballistamon<br>Shoutmonx2<br>Manticoremon<br>Bulkmon<br>Cerberumon<br>Darktyrannomon<br>Extyrannomon<br>Growmon<br>Megalogrowmon<br>Metaltyrannomon<br>Skullgreymon<br>Monzaemon<br>Omegashoutmon<br>Shoutmonx3<br>Raremon<br>Rareraremon<br>Dinobeemon<br>Goldnumemon<br>Megadramon<br>Cargodramon<br>Jazardmon<br>Jazarichmon<br>Rukamon<br>Seadramon</span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 style=\"color: #169179; text-align: center;\"><strong>REQUIRED TO RUN:</strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mods/cobblemon\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong><img style=\"color: #fff; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/620/286/64/64/638008832892634916.png\" alt=\"Cobblemon logo\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></strong></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #fff;\">Special thanks to:</span></strong><br><strong><span style=\"color: #fff;\">Modelers: Nexuss, Shy 72, Megadrive_Menace, Berriblast, SoulCarver106, Tymander, Ismael, Green Boi, Frigimon, Rin, Gwen, HavocZhou, TennyThomas1, KRverde, Cyber and Kissy Missies, Moodkip, Jawoon, MushroomFrog, CheolBong_E, Chasedownall, Ryastoise, MajorW, Noahred3603, vampirestarfish, Cris09 and Gumi.</span></strong><br><br></h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #fff;\">MajorSirius &ndash; Shiny textures &amp; additional GUI/model texture fixes</span></strong></h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><strong><span style=\"color: #fff;\">Nopesicle, Midmilk &amp; Emrys &nbsp;&ndash; Balancing assistance</span></strong></h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><strong><span style=\"color: #fff;\">Rex &ndash; Lore accuracy improvements</span></strong></h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><br><strong><span style=\"color: #fff;\">Animators: Carrot, Rallen Scallar, EYE, Ryastoise, </span></strong></h3>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #fff;\">TennyThomas1</span><span style=\"color: #fff;\">.</span></strong><br><br><strong><span style=\"color: #fff;\">&nbsp; Translators: Longsansuisui and Delkayah.</span></strong></h3>",
